title: Updates on Carolingian UI for v13
content:
Version 2.2.0:

  • Hide UI: Added settings that allow completely hiding interface elements.

Version 2.1.12:

  • Module Compatibility: Added style adjustments for modules from TheRipper93 and a few others.
  • Settings: Fixed bugs and adjusted issues with settings.

Check more on Discord or the Github repository.

Note: Version 2.x of Carolingian UI is for Foundry v13. If you are using v12, install version that starts with 1.
